      <section id="formatting-expectations">
         <title>Formatting expectations</title>
         <p>Processors typically use the following conventions:</p>
         <ul>
            <li>The content of each simple list item is placed on a separate line.</li>
            <li>The lines are not distinguished by numbers, bullets, or other icons.</li>
         </ul>
